{"word":"G1210 - δέω - déō - deh'-o - Bind","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">déō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">deh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bind</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கட்டு, காவல் பண்ணு, காவலில் வை"},{"paragraph":"to bind, tie, fasten"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A primary verb; to <i>bind</i> (in various applications, literally or figuratively): - bind, be in bonds, knit, tie, wind. See also <a href=\"#/G1163 - δεῖ - deî - die/1163\">G1163</a>, <a href=\"#/G1189 - δέομαι - déomai - deh'-om-ahee/1189\">G1189</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}